{"tid":648014,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"幫個小五學生補數 唔知點教好","createTime":"2018-04-30T10:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T01:20:18.000Z","uid":97299,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ac3c671495d6c762f4c1a9f5651c53e75aedd98f","tid":648014,"uid":97299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:22:32.000Z","msg":"呢份私補我都做左一個月，上過四堂<br />\n我由第一堂開始已經發覺佢天資聰敏架啦。<br />\n<br />\n問落原來呢位學生哥數學根本識晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，搵私補既原因係佢呀媽見佢考試唔小心做錯，失左幾分，就驚佢退步。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家我都唔知教咩好，預先教佢小六既課程，一方面佢唔太願意學，另一方面我又唔想chur佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而叫佢操exercise對佢黎講係輕而易舉，但係會搞到課堂好枯燥。<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打過來人可以分享下經驗/話我知應該點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：我數學底係唔錯，up to 基本calculus都識教"},{"pid":"3a2938448dee322b6fefbb44986f18f07c315d7d","tid":648014,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:26:29.000Z","msg":"小五學小六都唔過份呀 學中一就over啲"},{"pid":"6b3ee47f65ab9377596758d29402fa180b872255","tid":648014,"uid":135293,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:29:20.000Z","msg":"我個個成日錯d無謂嘢<br />\n小數點數錯 乘乘下變咗加數<br />\n又成日唔做數<br />\n做數就話要做英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed780e4766b69152a879117d1cea7e1daaf5eed8","tid":648014,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:30:35.000Z","msg":"諗吓點用有趣嘅方法教佢"},{"pid":"048ff6665f7d8bcc5bb2b9111214fdebba36875a","tid":648014,"uid":135293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:30:47.000Z","msg":"佢仲堂堂同我講佢好憎數學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老師我都最撚憎做數 但係都要做㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a29fb4fce000ea87d2056a1e5ff347e00ba35b","tid":648014,"uid":30081,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:35:17.000Z","msg":"做岩一條數 比av佢睇"},{"pid":"2bc8e45a9d43c7a4c7582a28d816848aeea55d0a","tid":648014,"uid":134687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:35:53.000Z","msg":"試下有冇再難D既題目可以教到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果冇既咪算囉，keep住個level已經夠啦"},{"pid":"3981e96079ae9bfb2bd6a16a6c9df7ea6e98d834","tid":648014,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:38:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0ea16ed73ef2db927ec999c880ebb07672bcde2","tid":648014,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:38:50.000Z","msg":"比佢打機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc4a290e77b2d95646d6dbb15d5156f6c13a314","tid":648014,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:38:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19c65a0f80ff7190b82a05c0cbba836b21ce691a","tid":648014,"uid":147952,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:41:01.000Z","msg":"就咁，9up嘅，<br />\n你試下俾啲難少少嘅數佢<br />\n叫佢邊做邊口頭解俾你聽 (啫係好似啲補習天王教書咁) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣你可以知道佢思維邊度出咗小問題 <br />\n另外呢種方法可以令佢更清楚自己點樣諗條題目同解法<br />\n而且一啲都唔悶，仲可以train埋佢講野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然，要睇你識唔識俾多啲feedback而唔係齋聽啦"},{"pid":"fa9ea5241fa0d17de8823660079b208e8db9351e","tid":648014,"uid":184509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:45:56.000Z","msg":"係咪奧數隊？玩奧數囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9a126439e5c4a64e740a5fbd9de57c0d3d508c","tid":648014,"uid":97299,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36a29fb4fce000ea87d2056a1e5ff347e00ba35b","tid":648014,"uid":30081,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:35:17.000Z","msg":"做岩一條數 比av佢睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:05:04.000Z","msg":"家長喺附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f984686acb85a0bc1f77bc8f46e31faa5df664","tid":648014,"uid":97299,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"3981e96079ae9bfb2bd6a16a6c9df7ea6e98d834","tid":648014,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:38:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:09:04.000Z","msg":"我試過教out-syl既數學, 例如將佢學既立體圖形教深入d<br />\n用平行線、垂直既概念去講2D、3D既「高」<br />\n佢就彈左句 : 小學生真係需要知呢d野?<br />\n我竟然無言以對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca54c8929aea5f6c4466e40442e3f62c90b4747","tid":648014,"uid":97299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3fc4a290e77b2d95646d6dbb15d5156f6c13a314","tid":648014,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:38:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:10:07.000Z","msg":"佢英文比較差既, 所以我有陣時用15分鐘同佢玩下英文flash game學下生字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5aea6e018a61f5e6960e3dc8491d47edd12961a","tid":648014,"uid":134845,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:11:29.000Z","msg":"我補緊個小四，佢老母成因想我教佢技巧 例如 做應用題見到咩字眼就用邊套方法咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2693c0e597e0165a3172c5f48f30b76a04be1333","tid":648014,"uid":142854,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:14:51.000Z","msg":"你呢種叫好<br />\n我補過d新移民<br />\nD數屎到一pat野咁 <br />\n問親佢d tricky野都係錯<br />\n例如 1米5厘米係105cm唔係150<br />\n講極話唔好錯都話識哂又剩<br />\n跟住問我休息得未<br />\n休息冇次準時返黎 之後再問又係唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606a916ff9170f7b32f597b8f1b06360f74b2f60","tid":648014,"uid":97299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"048ff6665f7d8bcc5bb2b9111214fdebba36875a","tid":648014,"uid":135293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T1